This folder contains 2 scripts which convert the AdventureWorks2022 DB tables and join relations into nodes and edges.
there is a script to run the multi-hop queries for testing

Required:
AdventureWorks2024 Database on your SQL Server 

Steps:
Run the following scripts by order
NodeTablesWithPopulation.sql
This script create node tables and populate data from AdventureWorks2022

EdgeTablesWithPopulation
This script create edge tables and populate data from AdventureWorks2022

Your SMSS should have nodes and table (see GraphTable.png)

Run the Multi-Hop-Query-Examples to see the results


